                            assertedValue="756"/>
                        <certainty match="../@value" locus="value"
                            assertedValue="757"/>
                        <certainty match="../@value" locus="value"
                            assertedValue="758"/>
                        <certainty match="../@value" locus="value"
                            assertedValue="759"/></num><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. There may be a trace before psi in line 2, but this is not certain. If this interpretation is correct, it indicates a love object whose name was valued isopsephistically at 750 or at a number in the range 751–759. There are at least seven feminine names in LGPN 5A in this range. Cf. Bagnall, R. S. et al., Graffiti from the Basilica in the Agora of Smyrna (2016): 48.
